Hey guys,
I have started a new en-devour in the avicus community. I have started a couples counseling group we currentley have 3 sets of partners and myself (the counselor) in the group. In the program we work through issues as a group and in individual sessions. This couples counseling program was created to help two individuals who are often sexually involved to work through their frustrations and problems with their partner. Please feel free to either sign up below or contact me personally on skype.
